text: Sudden Impact is 1983 American action thriller movie directed by Clint Eastwood (who also stars) and is the fourth movie in the Dirty Harry series. It also stars Sondra Locke, Pat Hingle, Bradford Dillman, Albert Popwell, Jack Thibeau, Bette Ford, Nancy Parsons and was distributed by Warner Bros. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1983 action movies Category:1983 thriller movies Category:1980s sequel movies Category:American action movies Category:American thriller movies Category:Warner Bros. movies Category:Movies directed by Clint Eastwood
